ashloo/|title='Marvel's The Punisher' Adds Actress Shohreh Aghdashloo|last=Goldman|first=Eric|publisher=[[Marvel Comics|Marvel.com]]|date=August 25, 2017|accessdate=August 28, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6t3ktKKQY?url=https://news.marvel.com/tv/72941/marvels-punisher-adds-actress-shohreh-aghdashloo/|archivedate=August 28, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ComicBookCast\">{{cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/2017/08/18/new-the-punisher-teaser-trailer-released/|title=New The Punisher Teaser Trailer Released|last=Davis|first=Brandon|publisher=ComicBook.com|date=August 18, 2017|accessdate=January 3, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6wCWpXkxG?url=http://comicbook.com/marvel/2017/08/18/new-the-punisher-teaser-trailer-released/|archivedate=January 3, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Plana\">{{cite web|url=https://bamsmackpow.com/2017/11/30/punisher-episode-13-review-memento-mori/|title=The Punisher episode 13 review: Memento Mori|last=McNulty|first=Mike|work=Bam! Smack! Pow!|publisher=[[Time Inc.]]|date=November 30, 2017|accessdate=January 3, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6wCWwJ91d?url=https://bamsmackpow.com/2017/11/30/punisher-episode-13-review-memento-mori/|archivedate=January 3, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FlickeringMythCast\">{{cite web|url=https://www.flickeringmyth.com/2017/11/punishers-showrunner-talks-frank-castles-nemesis-jigsaw/|title=The Punisher showrunner talks Frank Castle's nemesis Jigsaw and possible second season|last=Brace|first=Samuel|publisher=Flickering Myth|date=November 21, 2017|accessdate=January 3, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6wCWyXYM5?url=https://www.flickeringmyth.com/2017/11/punishers-showrunner-talks-frank-castles-nemesis-jigsaw/|archivedate=January 3, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Morgan\">{{cite web|url=https://screenrant.com/marvel-punisher-tv-show-turk/|title=Marvel's The Punisher Will Include a Turk Appearance|last=Hood|first