ers' Costume Details You Definitely Missed|last=Bundel|first=Ani|work=[[Elite Daily]]|date=September 1, 2017|accessdate=July 5, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/70g5zitMM?url=https://www.elitedaily.com/entertainment/the-defenders-costume-exclusive/2059296|archivedate=July 5, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LightfootColliderJul2018\">{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/the-punisher-season-2-interview-steve-lightfoot/|title=\u2018The Punisher\u2019 Showrunner Steve Lightfoot on Season 2, If He\u2019d Rather Do 10 Episodes, and More|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|date=July 4, 2018|accessdate=July 6, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/70h4cS6pQ?url=http://collider.com/the-punisher-season-2-interview-steve-lightfoot/|archivedate=July 5, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BustleEggs\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bustle.com/p/marvel-easter-eggs-in-the-punisher-season-1-tie-the-gritty-drama-to-its-comic-book-origins-5493176|title=Marvel Easter Eggs In 'The Punisher' Season 1 Tie The Gritty Drama To Its Comic Book Origins|last=Thomas|first=Leah|work=[[Bustle (magazine)|Bustle]]|date=November 17, 2017|accessdate=July 8, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/70kDE8oG8?url=https://www.bustle.com/p/marvel-easter-eggs-in-the-punisher-season-1-tie-the-gritty-drama-to-its-comic-book-origins-5493176|archivedate=July 7, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CosmicBookCast\">{{cite web|url=https://www.cosmicbooknews.com/new-punisher-netflix-poster|title=New Punisher Netflix Poster|last=McGloin|first=Matt|website=Cosmic Book News|date=May 31, 2017|accessdate=July 8, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/70kDJuDTx?url=https://www.cosmicbooknews.com/new-punisher-netflix-poster|archivedate=July 7, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Mahome\">{{cite av media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sTlxWPGVKiw|title=Episode 108 - Exclusive chat with Jordan Mahome of The Punisher and Ray Donovan|a