ly Man\"\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[44th Saturn Awards|Saturn Awards]]\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Actor on Television|Best Actor on Television]]\n| [[Jon Bernthal]]\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"2\" | <ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/saturn-awards-nominations-2018-black-panther-walking-dead-1202727752/|title=\u2018Black Panther,\u2019 \u2018Walking Dead\u2019 Rule Saturn Awards Nominations|last=McNary|first=Dave|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=March 15, 2018|accessdate=March 15, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6xwc1azco?url=http://variety.com/2018/film/news/saturn-awards-nominations-2018-black-panther-walking-dead-1202727752/|archivedate=March 15, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/saturn-awards-2018-black-panther-better-call-saul-twin-peaks-1202860077/|title=\u2018Black Panther\u2019 Reigns at Saturn Awards, \u2018Better Call Saul\u2019 and \u2018Twin Peaks\u2019 Top TV Field|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|last=McNary|first=Dave|date=June 27, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best New Media Superhero Series\n| ''[[The Punisher (TV series)|The Punisher]]''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award]]\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Stunt Coordination for a Drama Series, Limited Series, or Movie|Outstanding Stunt Coordination for a Drama Series, Limited Series, or Movie]]\n| ''The Punisher''\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.emmys.com/shows/marvels-punisher|title=Marvel's The Punisher SHOWS NOMINATIONS|website=Emmys.com|accessdate=September 9, 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|refs =\n\n<ref name=\"PunisherEWApr2016\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ew.com/article/2016/04/29/punisher-marvel-netflix |title=Marvel's The Punisher spin-off ordered by Netflix |last=Hibberd |first=James |work=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |date=April 29, 2016 |accessdate=April 29, 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6h8EeSR4U?url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/04/29/punisher-marvel-netflix?xid=entertainment-weekly_socialflow_twitter |archivedate=April 29, 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"MarvelOct2016\">{{cite web|url=http://marvel.com/news/tv/26831/netflix_original_series_marvels_the_punisher_announces_three_new_cast_members?linkId=29613508 |title=Netflix Original Series 'Marvel's The Punisher' Announces Three New Cast Members |publisher=[[Marvel Comics|Marvel.com]] |date=October 6, 2016 |accessdate=October 6, 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6l3qTwPKI?url=http://marvel.com/news/tv/26831/netflix_original_series_marvels_the_punisher_announces_three_new_cast_members?linkId=29613508 |archivedate=October 6, 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"MicroName\">{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/tv/marvels-the-punisher-photos/david-lieberman-a-k-a-micro-ebon-moss-bachrach/|title=Marvel's The Punisher: 12 New Photos From the Spin-Off Series|last=Li|first=Shirley|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|date=September 12, 2017|accessdate=September 12, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6tQW8ITqW?url=http://ew.com/tv/marvels-the-punisher-photos/david-lieberman-a-k-a-micro-ebon-moss-bachrach/|archivedate=September 12, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NewCastOct2016\">{{cite web|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/779785-five-more-join-the-cast-of-marvels-the-punisher#/slide/1 |title=Five More Join the Cast of Marvel's The Punisher |last=Perry |first=Spencer |publisher=[[ComingSoon.net]] |date=October 25, 2016 |accessdate=October 26, 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6lWx38J7t?url=http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/779785-five-more-join-the-cast-of-marvels-the-punisher |archivedate=October 25, 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Wilson\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bustle.com/p/whos-lewis-wilson-in-the-punisher-this-veteran-may-be-the-beating-heart-of-the-series-5478701|title=Who's Lewis Wilson In 'The Punisher'? This Veteran May Be The Beating Heart of the Series|last=O'Keefe|first=Jack|work=[[Bustle (magazine)|Bustle]]|date=November 2017|accessdate=January 3, 2018|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6wCW3gcr3?url=https://www.bustle.com/p/whos-lewis-wilson-in-the-punisher-this-veteran-may-be-the-beating-heart-of-the-series-5478701|archivedate=January 3, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NYCC2016\">{{cite web|url=http://www.cbr.com/nycc-iron-fist-cast-makes-first-ever-live-appearance/ |title=NYCC: Iron Fist Cast Makes First-Ever Live Appearance |last=Damore |first=Meagan |publisher=[[Comic Book Resources]] |date=October 8, 2016 |accessdate=October 9, 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6l7K6g1QZ?url=http://www.cbr.com/nycc-iron-fist-cast-makes-first-ever-live-appearance/ |archivedate=October 9, 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Aghdashloo\">{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/tv/2017/08/25/marvels-the-punisher-shohreh-aghdashloo/|title=Marvel's The Punisher adds Oscar nominee in recurring role|last=Li|first=Shirley|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|date=August 25, 2017|accessdate=August 25, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6sz8tYRj3?url=http://ew.com/tv/2017/08/25/marvels-the-punisher-shohreh-aghdashloo/|archivedate=August 25, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Aghdashloo2\">{{cite web|url=https://news.marvel.com/tv/72941/marvels-punisher-adds-actress-shohreh-aghdashloo/|title='Marvel's The Punisher' Adds Actress Shohreh Aghdashloo|last=Goldman|first=Eric|publisher=[[Marvel Comics|Marvel.com]]|date=August 25, 2017|accessdate=August 28, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6t3ktKKQY?url=https://news.marvel.com/tv/72941/marvels-punisher-adds-actress-shohreh-aghdashloo/|archivedate=August 28, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ComicBookCast\">{{cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/2017/08/18/new-the-punisher-teaser-trailer-released/|title=New The Punisher Teaser Trailer Released|last=Davis|first=Brandon|publisher=ComicBook.com|date=Aug